Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:03.98,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652.445,582)}Osaka\NTwo years later
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.72,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,172)}Mahjong New Maruko\NAll automatic tables
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I left Tokyo,\NJust wandering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a life,\Nbut after being here for six months
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I instead felt a longing to play Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Mahjong among friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,REAL Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his fifth straight win
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he's just too good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he lost？\N He's truly skillful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the sort that makes you hesitant to breathe, anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes you sit on pins and needles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive, kiddo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I like what I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lookin for a player like you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Care for a dink?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,An East/West contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The top ringers from *Kanto and *Kansai get together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:20.22,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,* Kantō is around Tokyo in the east of Japan\N*Kansai is around Osaka in the (so called) West
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an underworld Mahjong East/West battle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want me to join the West team?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no\NI ain't West
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is someone from the East team HERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This goes down here in Osaka TOMORROW, hell or high water!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our players didn't come in from Tokyo\NSo we're looking for someone strong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for players real quick, so I'm meeting with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My breh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he's the boss of the East team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My bro's on a different level
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong enough to win countless games
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. The East should win easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.28,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,It ain't that simple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The West has a monster of their own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,While being the Boss of the Kansai Yakuza
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he's also a ringer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada Katsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With his overwhelming money, power and connections
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's scouting for players of ability
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A monopoly on the skim
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Countrywide, each and every Mahjong parlor contributes a 10,000 Yen payment per day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That daily 10,000 yen payment amounts to 100 Million yen per day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for a full year
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You get *36.5 billion yen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:54.02,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,* More than 300 Million USD in 2019
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:58.42,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,A tale to set your heart dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it? Will you join the East camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta decide right away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to my brah right away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro is here right now playing a game with the West team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the guy I mentioned. The boss ringer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The West team head, Harada Katsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even among ringers he's indisputably a player of the highest level
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A genius that has been called the 2nd Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the head of the East team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My breh is playing there, right in front
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who dealt the invincible Akagi his only defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:04:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who with the strength of countless wins has repeatedly made the impossible possible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The head of the East team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:19.85,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,#/tv/shows linux ricing and online swimming lessons community presents:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:27.15,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,カンカン照り ギラついた \N太陽みたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:27.15,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Blazing hot, like the blistering sun
