Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.65,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,620)}Kishitani Goro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.81,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,あいつがまた帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.81,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,He's come back again
