Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.28,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766,608)}Furukawa Yuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:37.99,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,ざわざわと
