Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.95,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(528,510)}Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:49.01,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:49.01,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:55.01,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,くるくる廻る天道虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:55.01,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Ladybug going round and round
